<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome | Academy by PatSnap</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-/Y6pD6FV/Vv2HJnA6t+vslU6fwYXjCFtcEpHbNJ0lyAFsXTsjBbfaDjzALeQsN6M" crossorigin="anonymous"> <!-- load bootstrap css -->    
        <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<style>
  body{
    padding-top:65px;
  }

</style>

<body>
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><span class="fa fa-graduation-cap active" aria-hidden="true"></span>Academy by PatSnap</a>
   <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
  </button>
    <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
  <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
      <ul class=" navbar-nav mr-auto">
        <li class = "nav-item"><a href="/courses" class = "nav-link" >Courses</a></li>
        <li class = "nav-item"><a href="/profile" class = "nav-link" >Profile</a></li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
        <li class = "nav-item"><a href="/logout" class="nav-link">Logout</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div><!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
</nav>

<div class="container">
    <div class = row>
        <div class = "col-md-12">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
                <li class = "breadcrumb-item active">Home</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class = "row">
        <div class = "col-md-12">
          <div class=" border-top-0 border-left-0 border-right-0 border mb-2 ">
            <h1><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-education" aria-hidden="true"></span> Academy by PatSnap</h1>
            <h2> Welcome <%=user.local.profile.firstName%> </h2>
          </div>
        <div>
    </div>
    </div></div>
    <div class = "row">
      <div class="col-md-6 mt-2">
        <p>Fusce sed nibh diam. Maecenas facilisis lacinia ex vitae sodales. Aenean accumsan, enim non accumsan pharetra, ante erat consequat risus, vitae semper eros purus eget nisl. Vivamus ac aliquam arcu. Ut vitae iaculis est. Sed in pharetra eros, a tristique lacus. Mauris vulputate eleifend tristique. Sed vitae felis hendrerit, ullamcorper enim ac, suscipit augue. Nulla et tellus magna. Sed venenatis placerat mollis. Quisque semper eros quis scelerisque venenatis.</p>
        <a href = "/courses" class = "btn btn-primary" ><span class="fa fa-book active" aria-hidden="true"></span> Browse All Courses</a>
        <a href = "/profile" class = "btn btn-primary" ><span class="fa fa-user active" aria-hidden="true"></span> My Profile </a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 mt-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">Academy News</div>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">Under Construction</h4>
              <p class="card-text">New Academy is being built</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
     <div class = "row">
      <div class="col-md-12 mt-5">
      <h3><%=user.local.profile.firstName%>&apos;s Courses</h3>
      
      <%if(items.length){%>
      <table width='100%' class="table table-striped">
                <thead>
                    <th>Course Name </th>
                    <th>Progress </th>
                    <th></th>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% items.forEach(function(item){ %>

                   
                    <tr>
                        <td> <%=item.name%></td>
                        <td> <%=Math.round(item.progress)%> % </td>
                        <td> <a href = "/courses/<%=item.id%>" class = "btn btn-primary">Resume Course</a></td>
                    </tr>
                    <%});%>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <%} else {%>
            <p>You don't have any courses yet. <a href = "/courses">Get started here.</a></p>
            <%}%>
      </div>
    </div>


<script src = "//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-b/U6ypiBEHpOf/4+1nzFpr53nxSS+GLCkfwBdFNTxtclqqenISfwAzpKaMNFNmj4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-h0AbiXch4ZDo7tp9hKZ4TsHbi047NrKGLO3SEJAg45jXxnGIfYzk4Si90RDIqNm1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
